text: Pre-1927 Route 8 Spur was a route in New Jersey that ran from Dingman's Ferry east to Franklin Furnace, existing from 1926 to 1927. Today, it is part of the following routes: * County Route 560 (New Jersey) * U.S. Route 206 * New Jersey Route 15 * New Jersey Route 94 * County Route 631 (Sussex County, New Jersey) 08 Spur (pre-1927)
title: New Jersey Route 8 Spur (pre-1927)
